{"id":"lyr_6LW15a2m6ICM_MzY4Nw_0009","text":"我願你是女人 戀愛不發生","structure":{"line_index":9,"char_count":11},"semantics":{"themes":["性別困境","逃避","渴望解脫"],"sentiment":"NEGATIVE","keywords":["女人","戀愛不發生"]},"prosody":{"tone_pattern":[5,2,5,2,5,0,9,4,3,4,3],"tone_pattern_cantonese_jyutping":["ngo5","jyun6","nei5","si6","neoi5","jan4","lyun2","oi3","bat1","faat3","sang1"]},"nlp":{"tokens":[{"text":"我願","pos":"VERB"},{"text":"你","pos":"PRON"},{"text":"是","pos":"AUX"},{"text":"女人","pos":"NOUN"},{"text":"戀愛","pos":"NOUN"},{"text":"不","pos":"ADV"},{"text":"發生","pos":"VERB"}],"syntax_notes":"假設語氣「我願你是女人」，表達對性別角色的無奈，認為若對方是女人，這段痛苦的戀愛便不會發生。"},"source":{"title":"我恨我是女人","artists":["趙學而"],"lyricists":["張美賢"],"year":0,"genre":["情歌","悲傷情歌","廣東流行"]},"context_links":{"doc_id":"feitsui_3687","prev_line_id":"lyr_6LW15a2m6ICM_MzY4Nw_0008","next_line_id":"lyr_6LW15a2m6ICM_MzY4Nw_0010","paragraph_id":"para_03"}}
